## Added
* ANY vanilla explosion now create cloud and smoke particles
  * For some reason this effect was in the old versions of minecraft but not in 1.21.1
  * Check this video for showcase https://www.reddit.com/r/Minecraft/comments/1mp049m/after_6_years_mojang_has_finally_fixed_the/

## Changed
* Some collisions
* Improved gibbing
  * Iron golems now also turn into metal instead of fleshy chunks
  * Slimes can now be gibbed, turning into slime globs
  * Creepers now also gib into slime instead of blood

## Fixed
* Lightning issues in multiblocks
* 256k tank's render crashing on clients without iris